# =============================================================================
# Umbrella Git (wordpress_plugins): shared tooling + live-plugins manifest only
# =============================================================================
# Per-plugin and per-client source lives in its own repository under chameleon/,
# client/, plugins/, and archive/. Those trees are NOT tracked here — each
# folder typically has its own .git. Open a plugin folder as its own workspace
# when working on that product’s history.
# =============================================================================

# --- Per-repo source trees (own Git remotes) ---
/chameleon/
/client/
/archive/
/plugins/

# --- Optional root artefact ---
/dist/

# --- Secrets (never commit) ---
scripts/live-plugins-ftp.env

# --- OS / editor noise ---
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
.DS_Store
*.stackdump
